author: The Current
description:
Valerie June talks with The Current's Mac Wilson about 'Owls, Omens and Oracles'
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube or hit the Thanks button

Singer-songwriter Valerie June visited The Current studio to play solo acoustic versions of songs from her recent album, 'Owls, Omens and Oracles.' Afterwards, June sat down with The Current’s Mac Wilson to talk about the album and also to share her joyful spirit. “No matter what hard times we face, no matter what difficulties, challenges, we can create this beautiful world for others to appreciate long after we're gone,” June says. “And I think that's the goal.”

Watch and listen to the full interview above.

Valerie June’s 2025 album, Owls, Omens and Oracles, available on @FantasyRecordings.
